## Inputs & Outputs

**Inputs:**
- `obs_sequence` — list of integer observed state indices (0-indexed)
- `n_hidden_states` — number of hidden states N
- `n_obs_symbols` — number of distinct observation symbols M *(optional, auto-detected if not given)*

**Outputs:**
- `A` — Transition matrix (N × N)
- `B` — Emission matrix (N × M)
- `pi` — Initial state distribution (N,)
- `P(O|λ)` — Likelihood of the observation sequence
- `log_likelihoods` — List of log-likelihoods per iteration
- `history` — α, β, γ, ξ at each iteration *(printed for first 3 iterations)*
- `hmm_visualization.png` — All visualizations saved to disk

